commitResults.messageTitle: Add extension for Duke to accept natural dates
commitResults.messageBody:
Event and Deadline tasks now support natural date formats such as "mon", "tues"...."sun", "today", "tmr"

Users have the option to use natural dates in place of yyyy-mm-dd format when their input task is within 7 days from the current date.

getDateFromString method is added to the parent class Task for Event and Deadline to inherit, to avoid code duplication.
A new method getDateFromString was added to allow users to input natural dates.
